SUMMARY:Stay Play Kickoff Weekend
LOCATION:Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:Stay Play gets an early start this summer with the May 22-24 k
 ickoff weekend at five recreation centers across Tampa. Teens can head ove
 r from 6 pm-midnight for sports\, teen rooms\, music\, free food\, and mor
 e. The open Rec Centers this weekend are: Copeland\, 11001 N 15th St.\, 33
 612 Dr. Martin Luther King Jr. Center\, 2200 N Oregon Ave.\, 33607 Jackson
  Heights\, 3310 E Lake Ave.\, 33610 Springhill\, 1000 E Eskimo Ave.\, 3360
 4 Port Tampa\, 4702 W McCoy St.\, 33616 Additionally\, the Police Athletic
  League\, 1924 W Diana St.\, will be open for Midnight Basketball from 7-1
 1:30 pm. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/190671
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/190671
END:VEVENT
